原則，即在言論涉煽動暴力或有直接關係才招致懲罰，認為曾俊華的建議是嘗試汲取2003年立法的教訓，但對民主派而言不會輕易放下戒心。"},{"pid":"67d3265b9dfa8fe195faf499df725950059cfe53","tid":940823,"uid":30821,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"叫人投票俾泛民d 傻閪出嚟講兩句<br />\n班賤人入立法會點樣阻惡法通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5234f14de7c12f8b430558f2ebe5e60c7bf0fea","tid":940823,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"不如升埋旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀埋毛語錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d13089ad317aa02c8f11461fc0135baf43ecaa4","tid":940823,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"遲早宣完誓要唱國歌<br />\n邊個唱得差就係唔真誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92792c2f2e44f9dc88616b2276074331e9dd34ff","tid":940823,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"忠誠反對黨"},{"pid":"8a4c53ae9686a7b34b44e918890884fead1ae5fc","tid":940823,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"真係唔見棺材唔流眼淚"},{"pid":"a12a12112a56f27be35a7ddfad1810809435be9b","tid":940823,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"下次投票吸印仔吸屌你老母4隻字算"},{"pid":"5d80d6f894a7ee1c184e1accdf20b0802b42c54a","tid":940823,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都話泛民先係真正愛國愛港嗰班人嚟"},{"pid":"133f99fda134ccb2b3d876c2b8bd0a45c43ece90","tid":940823,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"民主黨最黑暗的一天"},{"pid":"46f0c42efcbafa6e2bd799ff30c526881f005b22","tid":940823,"uid":52651,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"d泛民打手去撚晒邊?"},{"pid":"edb6d016dd4aefdde5047f554f4